{"type":"message","id":"c95fffd1","parentId":"0be9ce1b","timestamp":"2026-03-08T18:40:59.920Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy is asking for a quick standup - what each Council member is focusing on today for DataFlow. She wants me to give a quick summary from each agent's perspective. Since the other agents aren't real separate sessions, I should voice them all in character but keep it brief and focused on DataFlow.\n\nThis is a good moment to be decisive and strategic as Rafael.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]\n\n🧭 **Council Standup — DataFlow Focus**\n\n**🔥 Uriel** — Validating OCR accuracy targets. Testing invoice extraction on 50 real Indonesian documents. Building the API integration scaffold for QuickBooks.\n\n**📣 Gabriel** — Mapping the bookkeeper persona. Drafting the product story: why DataFlow, not alternatives. Prepping testimonial video templates.\n\n**🤝 Raguel** — Recruiting first 5 bookkeepers for validation sprint. Building outreach sequences. Finding the ones willing to go on camera.\n\n**🛡️ Michael** — Risk audit on pricing model. Compliance check on data handling for Indonesian bookkeepers. Flagging VPS security gaps before sprint launch.\n\n**🧭 Rafael (me)** — Keeping everyone aligned on the 30-day sprint. Coordinating daily priorities. Making sure the Council's work feeds DataFlow, not diverges.\n\n**Bottom line:** You have 27 days. We're moving. What's blocking you right now? 🧭"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":334,"cacheRead":29396,"cacheWrite":43,"totalTokens":29783,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.00167,"cacheRead":0.0029396,"cacheWrite":0.000053750000000000005,"total":0.00467335}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772995254681}}
