{"type":"message","id":"665bd04c","parentId":"9b8db20d","timestamp":"2026-03-08T18:55:20.292Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy is asking me to set up a separate Telegram connection for \"agent Raphael\" with her own Telegram account. But I think she means a separate agent instance (one of the Council members). She said \"agent Raphael\" but I think she might mean one of the other agents, or she's testing if I can set up independent agents.\n\nActually, looking back at the context - I (Rafael) am already the main agent. She might be asking for each Council member to have their own Telegram connection so they can be contacted independently.\n\nBut wait - she said \"agent Raphael\" - that's me. Maybe she's confused about naming, or maybe she meant \"each agent\" - like Michael, Gabriel, Raguel, Uriel should have their own Telegram connections.\n\nI need to clarify what she's asking for. Does she want:\n1. Me (Rafael) to have a separate Telegram connection?\n2. Each of the other 4 Council members to have their own Telegram?\n3. Something else?\n\nI should ask for clarification rather than guess. Keep it direct and brief.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] I need clarity — do you want:\n\n1. **Each Council member** (Michael, Gabriel, Raguel, Uriel) to have their own separate Telegram accounts they respond from independently?\n\n2. Or **me** (Rafael) on a separate Telegram number so you can reach me directly without the chat interface?\n\nWhich one? 🧭"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":336,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":29443,"totalTokens":29789,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.00168,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.03680375,"total":0.03849375}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772996115188}}
