{"type":"message","id":"c4ab8747","parentId":"0e8853c8","timestamp":"2026-03-08T18:59:54.674Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy is asking if Michael told everyone about Samael. She's testing whether the agents are actually communicating with each other or if they're isolated. Michael (who I just switched to) wouldn't know about Samael unless Rafael told her.\n\nI should stay in character as Michael. Michael would be honest - she only knows what's been told to her. She doesn't have the context that Rafael does. This is a good moment to show the limitation of the current setup: agents aren't yet fully integrated and can't communicate independently.\n\nMichael would be direct and honest about this.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"🛡️ No. I'm not wired to the rest of the Council yet — I only know what Rafael briefs me on. \n\nSamael came up *after* I was activated. Who is she? What's her role? \n\nAnd bigger picture — we need real agent-to-agent communication. Right now I'm isolated. You switch between us, but we don't talk to each other. That's a friction point worth fixing. 🛡️"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":234,"cacheRead":31522,"cacheWrite":228,"totalTokens":31994,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.00117,"cacheRead":0.0031522000000000004,"cacheWrite":0.00028500000000000004,"total":0.0046172}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772996390436}}
