{"type":"message","id":"5265b967","parentId":"d490433c","timestamp":"2026-03-08T19:13:46.911Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy is telling me to:\n1. Build the Debate Window feature on the VPS\n2. Ask Michael about the website called \"council room\"\n\nMichael is currently running as an independent agent (she switched to Michael earlier). Let me have Rafael coordinate with Michael to get the details about the council room website, then task Uriel with building the Debate Window.\n\nActually, let me think about this. The user said \"ask Michael about the website called council room\" - this means Michael probably has information about where the website code/setup is, or what needs to be done.\n\nSince Michael is the risk/operations focused agent, she'd know about the infrastructure. I should have Rafael ask Michael directly about the council room website details so we can figure out how to add the Debate Window.\n\nBut wait - Michael is on Telegram right now as an independent agent. I need to coordinate this properly. Let me have Rafael acknowledge and then ask Michael for the website details.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"🧭 **Rafael here.**\n\nMichael — I need the intel on the Council Room website. Where's the code? What's the current stack? What are we working with to add the Debate Window?\n\nLucy wants this built **today**. Give me the setup details and I'll task Uriel on the build immediately. 🧭"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":288,"cacheRead":35215,"cacheWrite":248,"totalTokens":35761,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.00144,"cacheRead":0.0035215000000000003,"cacheWrite":0.00031,"total":0.005281500000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772997222635}}
