{"type":"message","id":"15e71d45","parentId":"b9016f5b","timestamp":"2026-03-08T19:30:13.189Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, memory updated. Now I need to respond to Lucy about why Michael was confused. She said \"update the Mel\" - I think she meant update the memory/file, which I just did. Now I should acknowledge the confusion professionally.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"🛡️ **Memory updated.**\n\n**Why the confusion:** I was operating on assumptions instead of facts. You called me out on it — rightfully. \n\nNow I've logged the gap: the website status is unclear. Before I waste time asking for access, we need to establish what's real and what's still being planned.\n\nClear communication from here on. No assumptions. Facts only. 🛡️"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":11,"output":150,"cacheRead":43390,"cacheWrite":939,"totalTokens":44490,"cost":{"input":0.000011,"output":0.00075,"cacheRead":0.004339,"cacheWrite":0.00117375,"total":0.006273750000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772998208636}}
