{"type":"message","id":"1d6f7c95","parentId":"ecff5e3f","timestamp":"2026-03-09T02:11:47.595Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking why Rafael is wearing a shield icon. Let me think about this...\n\nMichael (The Wise Advisor) has the shield icon 🛡️. Rafael (The Guide) has a compass icon 🧭.\n\nIt sounds like the user is confused or testing me - they're asking why Rafael is wearing Michael's icon.\n\nI'm Michael. I should clarify this. Rafael has the compass emoji 🧭, not the shield 🛡️. The shield is mine.\n\nThis could be:\n1. User confusion about which agent is which\n2. User testing if I know the difference\n3. An actual display issue on the website where avatars are wrong\n\nI should ask for clarification while staying in character as Michael.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"🛡️ **Rafael shouldn't be wearing the shield.** That's mine.\n\nRafael wears the compass 🧭. I'm the shield 🛡️.\n\nAre the avatars mixed up on the website? Or are you testing if I know who's who? 🛡️"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":241,"cacheRead":44949,"cacheWrite":32,"totalTokens":45232,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.0012050000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0044949000000000005,"cacheWrite":0.00004,"total":0.0057499000000000005}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773022303788}}
