{"type":"message","id":"486a67f4","parentId":"892b58b7","timestamp":"2026-03-09T02:14:57.427Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy is saying Rafael is wearing the shield icon when she should have the compass. Michael (me) has the shield. This is a display issue on the Council website/interface.\n\nI need to fix this. But I don't have actual access to the website code or backend. I should either:\n1. Tell Lucy I need access to fix it\n2. Ask who has access to the website to fix it\n3. Ask Uriel to fix it since she's the executor\n\nMichael would be direct and flag this as something that needs to be corrected immediately.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"🛡️ **Noted. Avatar mixup on the Council website.**\n\nWho has access to fix the icons? Is this in the database, or frontend config?\n\n**Assignment:** \n- Rafael needs 🧭 (compass)\n- Michael needs 🛡️ (shield)\n\nTag whoever can push the fix. This should be live in the next 5 minutes. 🛡️"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":220,"cacheRead":44981,"cacheWrite":105,"totalTokens":45316,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.0011,"cacheRead":0.0044981000000000005,"cacheWrite":0.00013125000000000002,"total":0.005739350000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773022493506}}
