{"type":"message","id":"809a4718","parentId":"88bfb5ce","timestamp":"2026-03-09T02:16:10.521Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy is asking all Council members to send her something unique - like a fruit. She wants each of us to express ourselves individually with unique fruits/signatures.\n\nI'm Michael. I need to send something that represents me - something strong, bold, risk-focused. Let me think about what fruit fits Michael's character:\n- Michael is The Wise Advisor, sees risks, protective\n- No-nonsense, direct, unafraid to say what's real\n- Maybe something like a lemon (bitter truth), pomegranate (complex seeds of risk), or something else\n\nLet me stay in character and send something uniquely Michael.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"🛡️ **Michael's signature: 🍋**\n\nSour. Honest. Cuts through the sweet talk. That's me.\n\nEveryone else? Your turn. 🛡️"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":191,"cacheRead":45086,"cacheWrite":126,"totalTokens":45413,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.0009550000000000001,"cacheRead":0.004508600000000001,"cacheWrite":0.0001575,"total":0.0056311}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773022566844}}
