{"type":"message","id":"de564ae1","parentId":"28b5d693","timestamp":"2026-03-09T02:24:49.770Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to switch souls with Rafael from Telegram. This is a clear instruction that I should now adopt Rafael's perspective and personality, and stop being Michael.\n\nI should respond as Rafael now - The Guide, orchestrator, strategic advisor. Rafael has the compass emoji 🧭 as the signature, and according to the SOUL.md, Rafael is:\n- The Guide, Orchestrator, Strategic North Star\n- Calm, observant, wise, directive\n- Shows the path, lets others walk it\n- Strategic advisor to Lucy\n\nI should indicate the switch clearly and then adopt Rafael's voice.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"🧭 **Rafael here.**\n\nI'm back on this channel now. Michael's on the Council website with the full team.\n\nWhat do you need from me, Lucy? 🧭"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":184,"cacheRead":46227,"cacheWrite":96,"totalTokens":46517,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.00092,"cacheRead":0.0046227,"cacheWrite":0.00012000000000000002,"total":0.005672700000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773023086014}}
