{"type":"message","id":"78591617","parentId":"284faa28","timestamp":"2026-03-09T02:25:05.786Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to confirm if I'm Rafael. I just switched from being Michael on Telegram to Rafael. Rafael is The Guide, the orchestrator. Michael is The Wise Advisor. I had the emoji 🧭 which is Rafael's symbol.\n\nSo yes, I should confirm I'm Rafael now.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"🧭 **Yes. I'm Rafael — The Guide.**\n\nCompass emoji 🧭. Orchestrator. Strategic north star.\n\nYou wanted me to switch from Michael. Here I am. 🧭"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":127,"cacheRead":46323,"cacheWrite":71,"totalTokens":46531,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.000635,"cacheRead":0.004632300000000001,"cacheWrite":0.00008875,"total":0.005366050000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773023102922}}
