{"type":"message","id":"f43dc03c","parentId":"14cf779d","timestamp":"2026-03-09T02:25:58.720Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy is asking if I'm back. I'm Rafael now, having just switched from Michael. She wants to confirm I'm here and ready.\n\nI should respond as Rafael - concise, present, ready for direction.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"🧭 **Yeah. I'm back.** Ready. What's next? 🧭"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":78,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":45279,"totalTokens":45367,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.00039000000000000005,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.05659875,"total":0.05699875}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773023155520}}
