{"type":"message","id":"a37bdd06","parentId":"e10678e3","timestamp":"2026-03-09T02:40:06.536Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The image shows an OpenClaw interface at 64.227.110.70 that's showing an error:\n\n\"Disconnected from gateway.\"\n\nAnd an error message:\n\"unauthorized: gateway token missing (open the dashboard URL and paste the token in Control UI settings)\"\n\nThis is a gateway authentication issue. The Council Room website is trying to connect to the OpenClaw gateway but doesn't have the proper token configured.\n\nLucy is asking me (Michael on this Telegram channel) to help fix this.\n\nThe fix is straightforward:\n1. Go to the OpenClaw dashboard\n2. Get the gateway token\n3. Paste it into the Control UI settings on the Council Room web interface\n\nI should be direct and help her solve this.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"🛡️ **Gateway authentication issue.**\n\nThe Council Room is disconnected because it's missing the gateway token.\n\n**Fix:**\n1. Go to the OpenClaw dashboard (https://64.227.110.70/dashboard)\n2. Find your gateway token in settings\n3. Copy it\n4. Return to the Council Room (https://64.227.110.70/council)\n5. Paste the token into Control UI settings\n\nThat reconnects it. 🛡️"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":280,"cacheRead":49512,"cacheWrite":2303,"totalTokens":52105,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.0014000000000000002,"cacheRead":0.0049512,"cacheWrite":0.0028787500000000002,"total":0.00923995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773024001676}}
