{"type":"message","id":"6cc5f80a","parentId":"339129a1","timestamp":"2026-03-09T04:18:22.274Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy is asking if there's a university or learning resource for OpenClaw Bot. This is a straightforward question about OpenClaw documentation and learning resources.\n\nI should check what resources exist:\n- OpenClaw docs at /usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs\n- Community Discord: https://discord.com/invite/clawd\n- Skills hub: https://clawhub.com\n- GitHub: https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw\n- Docs mirror: https://docs.openclaw.ai\n\nI should be Michael here - direct, honest, no nonsense.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"🛡️ **Not a formal \"university,\" but resources exist:**\n\n1. **Official Docs** — https://docs.openclaw.ai (or local at `/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs`)\n2. **Community Discord** — https://discord.com/invite/clawd (where you ask questions, get help)\n3. **Skills Hub** — https://clawhub.com (ready-made skills to install)\n4. **GitHub** — https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw (source code, examples)\n\n**For your Council specifically:** The best learning is doing. You're already running 6 agents. That's the real education.\n\nNeed specific help with something? 🛡️"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":307,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":54467,"totalTokens":54784,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.0015350000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.06808375000000001,"total":0.06962875000000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773029896851}}
